data.description: Back on Market through no fault of Seller - now with Brand New Carpeting throughout! Don't miss out on a second chance at this move-in-ready gem.Nestled in the heart of Moncks Corner this former model home built in the sought-after community of Fairmont South exemplifies modern living at its finest. This meticulously maintained residence combines sleek aesthetics with functional spaces, providing an unparalleled living experience.Boasting a striking contemporary design, featuring clean lines, large windows, and a neutral color palette, the open-concept layout creates a seamless flow between living spaces, allowing for both comfort and entertaining.The heart of this home is the gourmet kitchen, complete with state-of-the-art appliances, ample storage, and an expansive center island. It's an ideal space for culinary enthusiasts and casual family gatherings alike.  The first floor master suite is a sanctuary of luxury offering a spacious bedroom, walk-in closet, and a spa-like ensuite bath. The design exudes tranquility, providing a serene escape from the hustle and bustle of everyday life.    If that's not enough, the FROG can be used as a second master suite that's even more spacious and luxurious than the one downstairs.    So with multiple bedrooms and flexible living spaces, this home accommodates various lifestyles. Whether you need a home office, playroom, or guest suite, this home adapts effortlessly to your needs.  Step outside the home and you'll discover a private outdoor oasis, perfect for al fresco dining, gardening, or simply unwinding in nature. The backyard space offers endless possibilities for creating your own outdoor retreat.  This home is also loaded with energy-efficient features such as advanced insulation and high-quality windows, so you can enjoy a comfortable living environment while reducing your environmental footprint.  Fairmont South is a community offering a range of amenities for residents. From parks and walking trails to community centers and recreational facilities, there's something for everyone to enjoy.  Don't miss this opportunity to make 420 Fetterbush Dr your forever home.
